	* schema/CDebugger.exsd
	* src/org/eclipse/cdt/debug/core/ICDebugConfiguration.java
	* src/org/eclipse/cdt/debug/internal/core/DebugConfiguration.java
	Added supported CPU to Debugger extension.
	
